SECTION 7 — TERMINATION (หมวดที่ 7 — การยกเลิก)

7.1 This license is effective until terminated.

7.2 The Licensor may terminate this license immediately upon written notice
    if the Licensee:
    (a) Breaches any material term of this license;
    (b) Fails to make required revenue-sharing payments within 60 days of
        their due date;
    (c) Makes false or misleading revenue reports;
    (d) Uses the Software in violation of applicable law.

7.3 Upon termination:
    (a) All rights granted under this license cease immediately;
    (b) The Licensee must cease all use and distribution of the Software;
    (c) Outstanding revenue-sharing obligations remain enforceable;
    (d) Sections 5, 6, 7.3, and 8 survive termination.

